## 🔄 The 6-Phase Pipeline (How the system works)

```
Phase 1: KNOWLEDGE INGESTION
   ↓  Read all PDFs (ICAO, IOSA, Ops Manual, Amendments, Guidelines, Failures)
   ↓  Store in pgvector (AI search database)

Phase 2: TOPIC EXTRACTION
   ↓  Each agent reads its document and extracts training topics
   ↓  e.g. "Wind Shear Recovery", "TCAS Training", "Engine Fire"

Phase 3: MATRIX BUILDING
   ↓  All topics merged into one master EBT Matrix
   ↓  Each topic tagged with: frequency (6/12/36 months), mandatory?, source

Phase 4: RT ANALYSIS
   ↓  Read the pilot's RT PDF
   ↓  AI checks: "Was Wind Shear covered in this RT?"
   ↓  Result: topic-by-topic covered/not-covered

Phase 5: COMPLIANCE CHECK
   ↓  Compare RT history against frequency rules
   ↓  6-month topic missing → VIOLATION 🚨
   ↓  12-month topic approaching deadline → WARNING ⚠️

Phase 6: REPORTING
   ↓  Generate final compliance report
   ↓  Save to MongoDB + JSON + Excel
```

