## 👤 User Flows (Step by Step)

### Flow 1: First-Time Setup
```
Admin runs: python main.py
    ↓
App reads all knowledge docs (ICAO, IOSA, Ops Manual...)
    ↓
Builds EBT Matrix (list of all training topics)
    ↓
Saves matrix to MongoDB
    ↓
Dashboard shows matrix, awaiting first RT upload
```

### Flow 2: Upload a New RT (Most Common)
```
User opens Frontend UI
    ↓
Clicks "Upload RT" → selects PDF file
    ↓
Frontend sends: POST /api/upload-rt (with PDF)
    ↓
Backend saves PDF to uploads/ folder
    ↓
Background thread starts:
    1. Loads all previous RTs from MongoDB
    2. AI reads new RT PDF
    3. Checks each training topic: covered? yes/no
    4. Adds new RT to history
    5. Runs compliance rules on full history
    6. Saves results to MongoDB
    ↓
Frontend polls: GET /api/validation-status
    ↓
When done, Frontend shows: GET /api/dashboard
    ↓
User sees: ✅ Compliant / ⚠️ Warnings / 🚨 Violations
```

### Flow 3: View Compliance Report
```
User clicks "Compliance" in UI
    ↓
GET /api/compliance
    ↓
Shows: violations list, warnings list, topic timeline
    ↓
User can download: GET /api/compliance/download
```

### Flow 4: Download Matrix Excel
```
User clicks "Download Matrix"
    ↓
GET /api/matrix/download
    ↓
Returns formatted .xlsx file with all training topics
```

