## 📊 Compliance Rules (Simple)

| Topic Frequency | Rule | Consequence if missed |
|-----------------|------|-----------------------|
| Every **6 months** | Must be in EVERY RT | 🚨 VIOLATION immediately |
| Every **12 months** | Must appear in at least 1 of every 2 RTs | ⚠️ WARNING then 🚨 VIOLATION |
| Every **36 months** | Must appear at least once in 6 RTs | ⚠️ WARNING approaching, 🚨 VIOLATION if missed |

