## 🗄️ Database — What's Stored Where

### MongoDB (main database)
| Collection | What's stored |
|-----------|--------------|
| `RT_compliance_ebt_matrix` | All training topics (the matrix) |
| `RT_compliance_matrix_meta` | Matrix statistics & source counts |
| `RT_compliance_rt_analyses` | Results of each RT analysis |
| `RT_compliance_compliance_results` | Latest compliance check result |
| `RT_compliance_rt_uploads` | History of uploaded RT files |

### pgvector (AI search database)
- Stores **text chunks** from all knowledge documents
- Used by agents to do **semantic search** ("find topics related to wind shear")

### Azure Blob Storage (file storage)
- Stores the **knowledge PDF/Excel files** (ICAO docs, IOSA docs etc.)
- App downloads them at startup via `blob_storage.py`

