## 🔐 Authentication (Login System)

```
Frontend → Login via Azure AD (Microsoft login)
         → Gets a JWT token
         → Sends token in every API request header:
           Authorization: Bearer <token>
         
Backend  → Middleware checks token on every request
         → If valid → allow
         → If missing/invalid → 401 Unauthorized
         
Tests    → Set AUTH_ENABLED=false → skip auth check
```

